                 | (123) 465-6789
      #fh5co-about data-section="about"
        .fh5co-2col.fh5co-bg.to-animate-2 style=("background-image: url(images/res_img_1.jpg)")
        .fh5co-2col.fh5co-text
          h2.heading.to-animate About Us
          p.to-animate
            span.firstcharacter> P
            | aradise Biryani Pointe is the Pioneer and a successful Indian Restaurant Chain in USA knwon for its world class Authentic Hyderabadi Biryani. We   maintain excellence in taste and consistency by its unique recipe and Spice formula perfected over the years.We specialize in crafting mouth-watering food and providing superb customer service. Order online for pickup! We are and will always be with our customers and providing good and fresh foods witch are rich in required nutrients, and good and beneficial for the health of our precious customers.
            p.text-center.to-animate
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-outline href="#"  Check the Menu
      #fh5co-sayings
        .container
          .row.to-animate
            .flexslider
              ul.slides
                li
                  blockquote
                    p &ldquo;Cooking is an art, but all art requires knowing something about the techniques and materials&rdquo;
                    p.quote-author &mdash; Nathan Myhrvold
                li
                  blockquote
                    p &ldquo;Give a man food, and he can eat for a day. Give a man a job, and he can only eat for 30 minutes on break.&rdquo;
                    p.quote-author &mdash; Lev L. Spiro
                li
                  blockquote
                    p &ldquo;Find something youâ€™re passionate about and keep tremendously interested in it.&rdquo;
                    p.quote-author &mdash; Julia Child
                li
                  blockquote
                    p &ldquo;Never work before breakfast; if you have to work before breakfast, eat your breakfast first.&rdquo;
                    p.quote-author &mdash; Josh Billings
      #fh5co-featured data-section="features"
        .container
          .row.text-center.fh5co-heading.row-padded
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              h2.heading.to-animate Featured Dishes
              p.sub-heading.to-animate We know the way to your heart. Just allow us to take you on a fantastic food drive!
          .row
            .fh5co-grid
              .fh5co-v-half.to-animate-2
                .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/chicken_biryani.jpeg)")
                .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.fh5co-special-1.arrow-left
                  h2 Chicken Dum Biryani
                  span.pricing $10.99
                  p aromatic chicken | basmati rice | garam masala
              .fh5co-v-half
                .fh5co-h-row-2.to-animate-2
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/manchurian.jpeg)")
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.arrow-left
                    h2 Chicken Manchurian
                    span.pricing $9.99
                    p A traditional Chinese food made Indian way with aromatic spices and flavor.It's the best of both worlds and simply yummylicious
                .fh5co-h-row-2.fh5co-reversed.to-animate-2
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/res_img_8.jpg)")
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.arrow-right
                    h2 Chicken Tikka
                    span.pricing $8.99
                    p Thoroughly marinated meat cubes are cooked and then grilled on a skewer.
              .fh5co-v-half
                .fh5co-h-row-2.fh5co-reversed.to-animate-2
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/res_img_7.jpg)")
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.arrow-right
                    h2 Mirchi Ka saalan
                    span.pricing $7.99
                    p Long hot peppers cooked in sesame based sauce with garlic, onions and special spices
                .fh5co-h-row-2.to-animate-2
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/res_img_6.jpg)")
                  .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.arrow-left
                    h2 Paradise Fish Curry
                    span.pricing $11.99
                    p Hyderabadi Style Fish curry in special Paradise spice mix
              .fh5co-v-half.to-animate-2
                .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-bg-img style=("background-image: url(images/res_img_3.jpg)")
                .fh5co-v-col-2.fh5co-text.fh5co-special-1.arrow-left
                  h2 Qubani Ka Meetha
                  span.pricing $5.99
                  p A creamy delicious sweet made out of dried apricot, dates & rose petals served with ice cream
